        "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
        "body": "<p>I believe you have to configure you Identity on appsettings.json</p>\n<p>On dev you have</p>\n<pre><code>&quot;IdentityServer&quot;: {\n    &quot;Clients&quot;: {\n      &quot;updown&quot;: {\n        &quot;Profile&quot;: &quot;IdentityServerSPA&quot;\n      }\n\n    },\n    &quot;Key&quot;: {\n      &quot;Type&quot;: &quot;Development&quot;\n    }\n</code></pre>\n<p>But in production you must configure some certificates.</p>\n<pre><code> &quot;Key&quot;: {\n      &quot;Type&quot;: &quot;File&quot;,\n      &quot;FilePath&quot;: &quot;path to .pfx&quot;,\n      &quot;Password&quot;: &quot;pass&quot;\n    }\n \n</code></pre>\n<p>otherwise not recommended put the tempkey.json from obj folder</p>\n"
    },
